data.description: Come home to this charming 2 story home on a sleepy Cochranton side street. Sunny kitchen with plenty of room for a table in back or pull up chairs to the peninsula. Spacious living room, dining room/family sitting room with chandelier. First floor laundry room off the kitchen and an extra sitting/sewing room in front. 4 bedrooms each with lit closets, upstairs bathroom with whirlpool tub and laundry chute. Extra wide lot means plenty of room to play and entertain out back. Above ground pool. Large carport big enough for both vehicles, along with another carport and shed in back. New electric furnace & hot water tank 8/22.
